%description:
TCP F-RTO (Workstream D5, RFC 5682 SACK-enhanced): spurious-RTO detection and
undo. The client sends a 3000-byte flight (3 MSS segments); the tester deletes
every ACK the server sends for it (b2-b4), so the client's retransmission timer
fires even though ALL the data arrived at the receiver -- the canonical
spurious RTO (only the reverse path lost the ACKs).

On the RTO the client arms an F-RTO episode (undo context captured before the
ssthresh/cwnd reduction, frtoHighSeq = snd_max) and retransmits the head
segment. The server, which already holds all 3000 bytes, answers with a full
cumulative ACK of 3001. The segmentsAcked() scoreboard scan finds the range
[1001..3001) with transmitCount == 1 -- never retransmitted, so the original
transmissions must have been delivered -- proving the timeout spurious: the
pre-RTO cwnd/ssthresh are restored (undoCwndReduction) and the loss marks are
dropped.

Falsification: with frtoEnabled=false (verified during development), the same
scenario leaves the post-RTO cwnd at the slow-start value and the "F-RTO:
spurious" line never appears; the %not-contains on a second RTO also fails if
the undo accidentally rearms a bogus retransmission.

%inifile: omnetpp.ini
[General]
record-vector-results = false
ned-path = .;../../../../src;../../lib

network = inet.test.moduletest.lib.TcpTestNet1

cmdenv-event-banners=false
cmdenv-express-mode=false
cmdenv-log-prefix="[%c]: "

*.testing=false
*.tcptester.script="b2 delete;b3 delete;b4 delete"

*.cli_app.localAddress="10.0.0.1"
*.cli_app.localPort=1000
*.cli_app.connectAddress="10.0.0.2"
*.cli_app.connectPort=2000
*.cli_app.active=true
*.cli_app.tOpen=0s
*.cli_app.tSend=0.5s
*.cli_app.sendBytes=3000B
*.cli_app.tClose=-1s
*.cli_app.sendScript=""

*.srv_app.localAddress="10.0.0.2"
*.srv_app.localPort=2000
*.srv_app.connectAddress="10.0.0.1"
*.srv_app.connectPort=1000
*.srv_app.active=false
*.srv_app.tOpen=0s
*.srv_app.tSend=-1s
*.srv_app.sendBytes=0B
*.srv_app.tClose=-1s
*.srv_app.sendScript=""

*.*_tcp.windowScalingSupport = false
*.*_tcp.timestampSupport = false
*.*_tcp.mss = 1000
*.*_tcp.tcpAlgorithmClass = "TcpReno"
*.*_tcp.delayedAcksEnabled = false
*.*_tcp.sackSupport = true
*.*_tcp.frtoEnabled = true
*.*_tcp.initialWindow = "rfc6928"
*.*_tcp.advertisedWindow = 20000

include ../../lib/tcp-legacy.ini

%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%contains: stdout
F-RTO: spurious retransmission timeout detected, undoing the RTO response
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%contains: stdout
Undoing spurious cwnd reduction
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%postrun-command: grep -c "Performing retransmission" test.out > test_rexmit_count.out || true
%contains: test_rexmit_count.out
1
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%postrun-command: grep "undisposed object:" test.out > test_undisposed.out || true
%not-contains: test_undisposed.out
undisposed object: (
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
